    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Pro felicitate temporum beatorum <lb n="2"/>Quintus Cassius Taurus <expan><abbr>fl</abbr><ex>amen</ex></expan> p<expan><ex>er</ex><abbr>p</abbr><ex>etuus</ex></expan> Legalis <lb n="3"/>ob honorem flamoni paterni con<lb break="no" n="4"/>sensu splendidissimi ordinis sibi con<lb break="no" n="5"/>locati cenitatem curiam sum<expan><ex>p</ex><abbr>tu</abbr></expan> proprio </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> repparavit <note>sic</note>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Legalis dürfte Ethnikon, abgeleitet von Leges Maiorum, sein; J. Marcillet-Jaubert deutet legalis als Zusatz zu flamen perpetuus. Z.6 repparavit steht auf dem Rahmen.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography">
                <listBibl><bibl>AE 1982, 0961.</bibl><bibl>J. Marcillet-Jaubert, Epigraphica 41, 1979, 70-72; fig. 3. (C) - AE 1982.</bibl><bibl/></listBibl>
            </div>
        </body>
